text:
The message you sent me? There
was nothing on it. I was SUPER
worried. I thought maybe someone
stole the letters off your card?
But that's not a thing that can
happen, is it? Don't freak me out!

Um, so I got your blank message.
I thought it was weird...but then I
was like, I guess you don't need 
words to tell someone you care?
So, here's how much I care:
"_________"!

I got your blank message card.
This was my favorite part:
"_______________"!
Deep. Makes you think, you know?
